<a id="words"><h4>words ([number])</h4></a>
          <p>Splits the original text into words separated by whitespace and reformats the text with [number] words on each line. [number] defaults to 1 when omitted.</p>
          <p class="see-also">See also <a href="#twords">twords</a></p>
